AB  - The proceedings contain 161 papers. The topics discussed include: intelligent connected vehicle data security based on blockchain combining zero-knowledge proof and post-quantum cryptography; highway service area traffic forecasting based on multi-domain mixed temporal data pre-training; analysis on the distribution of the economy hotel guest flow in Wuhan based on the data of guest's check-in time; visual analysis of Liaoning province tourism spots data based on python in English context; application and research of particle swarm optimization algorithm in cloud data backup; construction and realization of modern Chinese vocabulary base driven by big data; research on financial data trend prediction based on deep learning; and development of a Python-based comprehensive employment data visualization platform.
