TI  - A Novel Quantum Chimp Optimization with DNA Sequence Based Multihop Secure Routing Protocol for Wireless Sensor Networks
PY  - 2024
T2  - Wireless Personal Communications
VL  - 136
IS  - 3
SP  - 1353
EP  - 1374
