TI  - A Multi-Level Simulation of GeH FETs: From Nanomaterial and Device Characteristics to Circuit Performance Optimization
PY  - 2022
T2  - Proceedings of the 17th ACM International Symposium on Nanoscale Architectures, NANOARCH 2022
C7  - 5
