AB  - The rapid development of the transportation in-dustry brings great challenge to airport taxiway routing. This paper presents a collaborative quantum inspired ant colony algorithm(CQIACA) for finding a reasonable solution to the airport taxiway routing problem. Theoretical analysis and simulation results shows that our algorithm performs better in terms of efficiency and effectiveness, and our algorithm is more suitable for actual needs. © 2021 IEEE.
