AB  - The proceedings contain 295 papers. The topics discussed include: thermally radiative casson fluid flow over a cylinder with newtonian heating and heat generation/absorption; pulsating flow of casson nanofluid through a channel with thermal radiation and applied magnetic field; a technique for encoding and decoding using matrix theory; the physical time in positive direction is associated with matters only whereas the physical time in negative direction is associated with anti – matters; visualizing non-covalent interactions between propylamine and 2-chlorobenzyl alcohol in benzene: theoretical and dielectric relaxation studies; cybersecurity in the quantum era - a study of perceived risks in conventional cryptography and discussion on post quantum methods; an efficient scheme for reliable file transfer using residual link lifetime estimation based on sparse vehicular routes; random forest-based method for micro grid system in energy consumption prediction; machine learning-based optimization technique for forecasting the solar radiation; an efficient framework of human voice verification for robotic applications; design and implementation of wide band for biconical antenna for X band applications; experimental investigation on geo polymer concrete cubes with ambient and sunlight curing; experimental investigation of light weight aggregate with internal curing agent by using fly ash aggregate; and network simulation software architecture of blockchain: a model-led viewpoint.
