TI  - Visible and Near Infrared Spectral Analysis of the Lubricating Oil Dynamic Viscosity Based on Quantum Genetic-Neural Network Algorithm
ST  - 量子遗传-神经网络算法的润滑油动力粘度值可见近红外光谱分析
