TI  - Angle resolved photoemission spectroscopy studies on three dimensional strong topological insulators and magnetic topological insulators
ST  - 强三维拓扑绝缘体与磁性拓扑绝缘体的角分辨光电子能谱学研究进展
PY  - 2019
T2  - Wuli Xuebao/Acta Physica Sinica
VL  - 68
IS  - 22
C7  - 227901
