AB  - Quantum-behaved Particle Swarm Optimization (QPSO) algorithm is employed to solve route planning problems in view of premature convergence of Particle Swarm Optimization (PSO) algorithm. The simulation results show that compared with PSO, QPSO has stronger global search ability and faster convergence speed. The feasibility and efficiency of QPSO on route planning is proved. © 2014 IEEE.
