TI  - Application of geographic information system for water distritbution networks through quantum gis plug-in with hydraulic simulation for infrastructure and development planning
PY  - 2017
T2  - 38th Asian Conference on Remote Sensing - Space Applications: Touching Human Lives, ACRS 2017
VL  - 2017-October
