AB  - The proceedings contain 68 papers. The topics discussed include: modeling on current-voltage characteristics of HgCdTe photodiodes in forward bias region; simulation of InGaN/GaN light-emitting diodes with a non-local quantum well transport model; simulation of InGaN/GaN light-emitting diodes with patterned sapphire substrate; two-dimensional simulation of mid-infrared quantum cascade lasers: temperature and field dependent analysis; the hybridization of plasmons in GaN-based two-dimensional channels; structure design of refractive index sensor based on LPFG with double-layer coatings; polarization-independent self-collimated beam splitting in two-dimensional photonic crystals; optimization of InSb infrared focal plane arrays; a bisection-function technique to characterize heat transport in high-power GaN-based light-emitting-diodes package; and physical model of an optical memory cell with coupling quantum dots.
