AB  - It is difficult to obtain the satisfactory solution because traffic information is far less than the number of on variables. This paper presents a method based on Quantum-behaved Particle Swarm Optimization (QPSO) algorithm to obtain the global optimal solution. It designs the method based on QPSO algorithm to solve the on matrix prediction model, lists the detailed steps and points out how to choose the PSO operator. And then uses MATLAB programming language to carry out the simulation test. The simulation results show that the method has higher efficiency and accuracy. ©2009 IEEE.
