TI  - Quantum evolutionary algorithm for capacitated vehicle routing problem
PY  - 2009
T2  - Xitong Gongcheng Lilun yu Shijian/System Engineering Theory and Practice
VL  - 29
IS  - 2
SP  - 159
EP  - 166
