TI  - QoS multicast routing approach based on parallel quantum genetic algorithm
PY  - 2007
T2  - Nanjing Youdian Daxue Xuebao (Ziran Kexue Ban)/Journal of Nanjing University of Posts and Telecommunications (Natural Science)
VL  - 27
