AB  - The proceedings contains 220 papers from the 2004 NSTI Nanotechnology Conference and Trade Show - NSTI Nanotechnology 2004 - Technical Proceedings: Volume 2. The topics discussed include: spectral analysis of channel noise in nanoscale MOSFETs; a technology-independent model for nanoscale logic devices; principles of metallic field effect transistor (METDET); sub-threshold electron mobility in SOI-MESFETs; extraction of extrinsic series resistance in RF CMOS; on the correlation between model process parameters in statistical modeling and Pareto-optimal modeling for efficient PLL optimization.
