AB  - For the design and optimisation of modern quantum well based opto-electronic devices, a numerical simulator is required. This paper describes such a simulator. It includes the carrier transport through the quantum wells as well as the optical gain and the propagation of a light flux. This simulator is then used for the simulation of multi quantum well semiconductor optical amplifiers. © 1994, MCB UP Limited. All rights reserved.
